OL,3,COllie Davis: Dad jailed for murdering
OL,4,Cbaby son who suffered broken neck
OL,6,FA father has been sentenced to life in
OL,7,Fprison for murdering his five-week-old
OL,8,Fbaby, who died from a broken neck.
OL,10,FOllie Davis was found lifeless in his
OL,11,Fcrib at home in in October 2017, with
OL,12,Ffractures to his skull, collar bone,
OL,13,Fboth arms and the joints of all his
OL,14,Flimbs.
OL,16,FThe judge, sitting at Loughborough
OL,17,FCourt, said medical experts had
OL,18,Fconfirmed that Ollie suffered 23 rib
OL,19,Ffractures and other injuries usually
OL,20,Fseen after a "high energy car crash."
