OL,6,FHe was taken by ambulance to where he
OL,7,Fdied later that day.
OL,9,FJudge Justice Cotter said Ollie would
OL,10,Fhave been in "significant pain" in the
OL,11,Fdays leading up to his death.
OL,13,FMichael Davis, 29, was sentenced to
OL,14,Flife in prison with a minimum term of
OL,15,F22 years.
OL,17,FThe baby's mother, Kayleigh Driver,
OL,18,F31, was cleared of murder last month
OL,19,Fbut found guilty of causing or
OL,20,Fallowing her son's death.
