OL,6,FDriver has been jailed for seven years
OL,7,Ffor allowing the death of a child and
OL,8,Fallowing serious physical injury.
OL,10,FSentencing Michael Davis, formerly of
OL,11,FUpper Temple Walk, Leicester, Mr
OL,12,FJustice Cotter said the murder of
OL,13,FOllie had involved a "devastating"
OL,14,Ffatal spinal injury inflicted up to
OL,15,Feight days before death.
