OL,6,FAfter saying he was sure that Davis
OL,7,Fhad caused all the injuries during
OL,8,Ffour separate overnight "episodes" of
OL,9,Fviolence, Mr Justice Cotter added: "At
OL,10,Fleast five different mechanisms were
OL,11,Frequired to cause this terrible array
OL,12,Fof injuries.
OL,14,F"Michael Davis, I have no doubt that
OL,15,Fduring the night you became frustrated
OL,16,Fand angry and this led to terrible
OL,17,Fviolence.
