OL,3,COllie Davis: Dad jailed for murdering
OL,4,Cbaby son who suffered broken neck
OL,6,FDuring a two-month trial into Ollie's
OL,7,Fmurder, the Crown's barrister, Jonas
OL,8,FHankin KC, told the jury: "A broken
OL,9,Fneck was not the only injury Ollie
OL,10,Fsustained. Medical investigation
OL,11,Frevealed Ollie had sustained a total
OL,12,Fof 37 fractures.
OL,14,F"They included fractures to the skull,
OL,15,Fhis collar bone, both arms between the
OL,16,Fshoulder and the elbow, 23 rib
OL,17,Ffractures and fractures to the joints
OL,18,Fof all four limbs.
