OL,4,Cbaby son who suffered broken neck
OL,6,F"He also suffered brain injuries,
OL,7,Fbleeding over the surface of the
OL,8,Fbrain."
OL,10,FThe injuries were inflicted over
OL,11,Fvarious overlapping time-frames of up
OL,12,Fto 10 days before death, the court
OL,13,Fheard.
OL,15,FMr Hankin continued: "Ollie could not
OL,16,Fhave caused the injuries to himself `
OL,17,Fhe was a five-week-old pre-mobile
OL,18,Fbaby."
