OL,6,FIn videoed police interviews, which
OL,7,Fwere released by Leicestershire Police
OL,8,Fafter the verdicts, Davis repeatedly
OL,9,Finsisted he could not account for
OL,10,FOllie's injuries.
OL,12,FClaiming his son had appeared
OL,13,F"peaceful" while asleep in his cot,
OL,14,FDavis said of the neck fracture: "We
OL,15,Fwill see how it's happened. He seemed
OL,16,Ffine when he was sleeping. He wasn't
OL,17,Facting any differently."
