OL,3,COllie Davis: Dad jailed for murdering
OL,4,Cbaby son who suffered broken neck
OL,6,FMichael Davis, 29, was found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurder and two counts of causing
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm and was remanded
OL,9,Fin custody facing a mandatory life
OL,10,Fsentence.
OL,12,FJurors cleared Ollie's mother,
OL,13,FKayleigh Driver, 31, of murder and
OL,14,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,15,Fintent, but found her guilty of
OL,16,Fcharges of causing or allowing the
OL,17,Fdeath of a child and causing or
OL,18,Fallowing serious physical injury.
